{# Audit Profile — extracted from financial.html.j2 #}
<h3>Audit Profile</h3>
{{ kv_table([
  {'key': 'Auditor', 'value': fin.auditor_name | format_na},
  {'key': 'Big 4', 'value': fin.is_big4 | format_na},
  {'key': 'Tenure', 'value': fin.auditor_tenure | format_na},
  {'key': 'Material Weaknesses', 'value': fin.material_weaknesses|default(0)},
  {'key': 'Going Concern', 'value': fin.going_concern|default('No')},
], title="Audit") }}
{# Audit profile interpretation #}
<ul class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 mb-3 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-4 space-y-0.5">
  {% if fin.is_big4 == 'Yes' and fin.material_weaknesses|default(0)|int == 0 and fin.going_concern|default('No') == 'No' %}
  <li>Clean audit opinion from a Big 4 firm with no material weaknesses and no going concern&mdash;strong D&amp;O protective factor that significantly reduces restatement and financial misrepresentation risk</li>
  {% elif fin.material_weaknesses|default(0)|int > 0 %}
  <li>Material weakness in internal controls is a significant D&amp;O risk factor&mdash;increases exposure to securities fraud allegations and shareholder derivative claims</li>
  {% endif %}
  {% if fin.auditor_tenure and fin.auditor_tenure != 'N/A' %}
  {% set tenure_num = fin.auditor_tenure|replace(' years', '')|replace(' year', '')|int(default=0) %}
  {% if tenure_num > 20 %}
  <li>Long auditor tenure ({{ fin.auditor_tenure }}) may raise auditor independence concerns per ISS and proxy advisory guidelines</li>
  {% elif tenure_num >= 5 %}
  <li>Auditor tenure of {{ fin.auditor_tenure }} is within normal range, indicating stable audit relationship</li>
  {% endif %}
  {% endif %}
</ul>
